column1: Heart and artery diseases such as angina and heart attack
Kidney diseases such as kidney failure
Liver diseases such as viral hepatitis and cirrhosis
Internal cancers such as stomach cancer and colon cancer
Respiratory system diseases such as asthma and chronic obstructive pulmonary disease (COPD)
Digestive system diseases such as intestinal ulcers and acute bowel inflammation
Bacterial infections such as strep throat and urinary tract infection
Viral infections such as colds and influenza
Various blood disorders such as anemia
